Carrie Kei Heim https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carrie_Kei_Heim 0 Carrie Kei Heim (born December 7, 1973) is an American actress, lawyer, and writer. She is best known for her roles as Cornelia in Santa Claus: The Movie (1985) and Nikki Ferris in The Parent Trap II (1986). After completing The Parent Trap ll, Carrie retired from acting.
